ai-patthana16.89:0.2_0: Having given the immaculateness of the Dhamma
ai-patthana16.89:0.3_0: for one who is attached to the donors of the forms,
ai-patthana16.89:1.1_0: One doesn’t give rise to the scope of visible in this way.
ai-patthana16.89:2.1_0: One doesn’t give rise to the scope of logic, or in the formless realm.
ai-patthana16.89:2.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
